overview.en: EZDex development team united with community development forces to deeply cultivate the underlying technology, and through the value transfer protocol (Value Transfer Protocol), proposed and implemented a series of technological upgrades and innovative solutions. Build a sustainable public blockchain blockchain.
overview.zh: EZDex开发团队与社区发展力量紧密合作，深耕基础技术，并通过价值转移协议（Value Transfer Protocol）提出并实施了一系列技术升级和创新解决方案。 建立可持续的公共区块链。
